data.description:
A documentary introducing CCM Miami Rental Solution on prime time French TV Turbo M6 channel in January 2013 with #1 French Rapper La Fouine Test drive with our brand new Porsche Carrera S convertible > http://www.ccmmiami.com/listing/rent-porsche-carrera-s-911/ with Laouni Mouhid ( La Fouine )

Turbo is the French equivalent to Top Gear in England, Speed TV in the US.
